game.name: Outcome
game.description:
One of the latest free online games to play for boys, Outcome is an ultimate treat for all platform distance gamer lovers. In this extremely popular adventure game, you have to react fast against the suddenly coming obstacles and reach the end of the level with your full confidence. You can use the space key to jump your character. While you can press Z or click to switch to the other side of the game level. 

In this highly-challenging and interesting game, your aim is to find your way through a land with no man and equipped with countless obstacles. The key to reaching the advanced levels of this game is to apply all your gaming skills, visit many survival camps in order to collect the optimum possible coins. In this endless running game, you have to run through the world filled with unlimited hindrances and survive. 

Overcome your obstacles by jumping over them confidently. Do not forget to collect the warp coins in order to reach the advanced level of this black and white distance game. Remember to run towards the end line while embarking on a fascinating journey. Either jump over the hindrances that come on your way or switch sides to help yourself run continuously and reach safely to the final destination. 

The outcome is a cool and easy-to-play platformer distance game which primary includes two controls: Jump and switch. You can pass through all the obstacles and hazards easily by jumping over them with the ?Jump? option. While your character can switch between the two platform sides by opting for the ?Switch? option. You will be awarded an opportunity to purchase new areas with the help of warp coins you have collected throughout your way.
